tes for a dinosaur-era fuel source.</Para></LeadPara></HandL><TailParas fid="td"><Para>If Singapore is to stay competitive globally, we should leverage our culture of innovation and human expertise to develop more efficient ways of capturing, generating, storing and distributing renewable energies.</Para><Para>Adam Reutens-Tan</Para></TailParas><Byline fid="by" index="field"></Byline><Credit fid="cr" index="field"></Credit><Contact fid="ct" index="field"></Contact><Notes fid="rf" index="field"></Notes><Art fid="art" index="field"></Art><Copyright fid="cy" index="field">(c) 2018 Singapore Press Holdings Limited </Copyright></Article></ArchiveDoc><AdocTOC adoctype="article"><Item size="0" ref="distdoc:archive/ArchiveDoc::Article" type="arttext"></Item><Item size="0" ref="distdoc:archive/InvertText" type="invtext"></Item></AdocTOC></DistDoc>

